<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/612695-does-anybody-know-whether-zane-grey-wrote">Does anybody know whether Zane Grey wrote a sequel to this book? I&#39;m still dangling and wondering how they did in their entrapment.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_612695'><a id="like_count_community_question_612695" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/612695?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F90160.Riders_of_the_Purple_Sage">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/612695-does-anybody-know-whether-zane-grey-wrote">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/612695-does-anybody-know-whether-zane-grey-wrote">See all 4 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/8646256-john"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_100x100-c7bfe730633c9983e27caaa66a8e244a.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/8646256-john">John</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Just to get a different version of it, look for the 1918 [=silent] movies Riders of the Purple Sage, and The Rainbow Trail. <br/>As mentioned, the latter h<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Just to get a different version of it, look for the 1918 [=silent] movies Riders of the Purple Sage, and The Rainbow Trail. <br />As mentioned, the latter has had different names. While Grey claimed it was not a sequel, it does tell what happened to the three trapped in the canyon, so most places call it a sequel.<br />The first (Purple Sage) has had many remakes ('18, '25, '31, 41, '44, '96).<br />The other (Rainbow Trail) not so many ('18, '25, '32).<br />So in film, only the first three Purple Sage's have a sequel [unless with a different name]. [I know nothing about The Desert's Crucible (1922) - is it unrelated?]<br />As mentioned by BG, The Desert Crucible is the same book as The Rainbow Trail, though the 2003 Desert Crucible is based on the original ms, not on the published 1915 version. [The Wikipedia article The Rainbow Trail says that the original title in 1915 was The Rainbow Trail, but they include a photo of the May, 1915 cover of The Argosy, which uses the title The Desert Crucible!]<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

