<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/688492-actually-this-is-a-question-about-another">Actually this is a question about another Zane Grey novel. What is the Zane Grey Western where the hero is a shy fellow [maybe named Cole?} and the heroine is an Eastern girl who is too flirty for the cowboy community and gets a bad reputation. He sort of kidnaps her and they end up in a forced, but sham, marriage. Eventually of course, she falls in love with him and the marriage become real.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_688492'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F90160.Riders_of_the_Purple_Sage">like</a></span>

