<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/136042683-gabriele-mencagli"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/136042683-gabriele-mencagli">Gabriele Mencagli</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The book is &quot;Code of the West&quot;. The name of the heroine is &quot;Georgie&quot; and the fellow was &quot;Cal&quot;.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The book is "Code of the West". The name of the heroine is "Georgie" and the fellow was "Cal".<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
