    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2602635783" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12631024976651140935">This was an enjoyable read which reminded me of old-fashioned western movies. The rating is actually three and a half stars.</span>

          </span>
