      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/2663060-riders-of-the-purple-sage">Quotes from Riders of the Pur...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
